AmaZulu Queen Shiyiwe Mantfombi Dlamini Zulu has passed away. eNCA's Siphamandla Goge is following developments. Courtesy #DStv403 KWANONGOMA - AmaZulu Queen Shiyiwe Mantfombi Dlamini Zulu has passed away. Prime Minister of the Zulu Monarch, Mangosuthu Buthelezi confirmed the news on Thursday night. READ: Queen Mantfombi MaDlamini Zulu to be interim leader of Zulu nation He's assured the nation that there will be no leadership vacuum in the Zulu nation. The queen's death comes just weeks after AmaZulu King Goodwill Zwelithini passed away.